WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.509 --> 00:00:01.554
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.554 --> 00:00:04.289
I'm excited to be with you all today.

00:00:04.289 --> 00:00:15.537
I have another cool prophetic visitation, vision, dream, or whatever you want to call it, from someone who sent it to me: Mina Jones.

00:00:15.537 --> 00:00:17.406
I'm excited about this one.

00:00:17.406 --> 00:00:28.560
This is actually about the Rapture and us transforming into our glorified bodies and being swept away by the Lord Jesus.

00:00:29.170 --> 00:00:31.720
I'm excited about it; I love stuff like this.

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:37.514
I just want to encourage you all: Jesus is coming.

00:00:37.514 --> 00:00:41.030
Jesus is coming, and He's coming sooner than people realize.

00:00:42.509 --> 00:00:47.925
I'm excited about the revival that I believe is going to be short-lived.

00:00:47.925 --> 00:00:58.799
It won't be a long, drawn-out end-time move, but I believe it will be a major harvest of souls that will be a quick thing.

00:00:59.519 --> 00:01:06.866
The wave will hit just like any wave; a wave does not linger, it just comes right in, washes on the shore, and pulls back.

00:01:07.488 --> 00:01:14.760
I believe we're going to see one last major push for souls right before the catching away of the church.

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:25.905
I really do believe we're going to see this with healings, signs, wonders, and demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of the Lord upon this earth through the remnant.

00:01:26.355 --> 00:01:28.199
I believe it could happen this summer.

00:01:28.199 --> 00:01:35.895
If it starts in May, June, or July, we could be out of here by October.

00:01:35.895 --> 00:01:45.018
I really truly believe that's the kind of window we would have—a six-month window, maybe—and then boom, we're caught up and taken away.

00:01:47.839 --> 00:01:54.849
Like I said, we're probably going to be here longer, but I'm just saying that's how fast I believe Jesus could come.

00:01:55.885 --> 00:02:02.222
Be watching and waiting; the signs of the times show things happening at a rapid pace every day.

00:02:02.222 --> 00:02:05.880
I'm going to let my wife read this to you all, and I hope it blesses you.

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:06.977
Hi, good morning everybody.

00:02:07.251 --> 00:02:12.631
I'm going to be reading this that was sent to us, so we'll just get right into it.

00:02:12.631 --> 00:02:35.177
'I want to share with you what the Lord allowed me to see regarding the Rapture, harpazo, Greek: to seize upon, to snatch away, or to take to oneself, found three times in the New Testament: Acts, 2 Corinthians 12:2-4, 1 Thessalonians, and Revelation 12:5.

00:02:35.177 --> 00:02:40.760
At first, I was allowed to experience the catching away.

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:47.560
I heard a loud sound; it was that of a trumpet, but more like a shofar.

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:57.417
I was looking up at the sky and remember seeing the clouds part as a glowing light broke through.

00:03:01.307 --> 00:03:01.631
I began to ascend quickly.

00:03:03.133 --> 00:03:10.920
I remember calling the name of the Lord over and over as it seemed I was picking up speed.

00:03:23.507 --> 00:03:24.113
I saw others, but I couldn't see them clearly; it was like I saw white silhouettes of people being pulled up with me.

00:03:24.113 --> 00:03:35.293
Perhaps this had to do with the transformation that takes place, mentioned by the Apostle Paul in 1 Corinthians.

00:03:35.293 --> 00:03:38.434
It's so beautiful, I can't wait.

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:45.139
I then found myself in a place, a Great Hall full of people.

00:03:46.839 --> 00:03:50.799
There was a quiet hum of chatter, and somehow peace radiated from it.

00:03:50.799 --> 00:03:57.622
It was the voices of the people greeting one another with joy.

00:03:57.622 --> 00:04:09.028
I looked through the endless crowd and noticed that to my right there was a more dense crowd, as if they were surrounding someone.

00:04:09.028 --> 00:04:13.540
My attention was drawn towards them.

00:04:13.540 --> 00:04:21.849
As my focus became directed at them, the crowd began to disperse.

00:04:21.849 --> 00:04:34.617
They made a pathway of sorts, almost like they read the curiosity of my mind to know who they were gathered around.

00:04:34.617 --> 00:04:42.704
As the path cleared, there He stood: Yeshua, dressed in a beautiful floor-length white robe that seemed to shimmer with light.

00:04:42.704 --> 00:04:48.840
He had a gold crown upon His head and a gold sash tied around His waist.

00:04:48.840 --> 00:04:51.040
He was absolutely stunning and beautiful.

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:55.980
We made eye contact, but I chose not to approach Him.

00:04:55.980 --> 00:05:23.880
I've often said to the Lord that if I made it home—if I had done enough to please Him in this life that He saw fit to allow me to return to Him—all I wanted was to just be able to make eye contact with Him, and the only thing I wanted in return was a smile.

00:05:23.880 --> 00:05:25.553
That's all I needed.

00:05:39.229 --> 00:05:39.684
It would be our way of communicating, our way of simply saying, "I made it.

00:05:39.684 --> 00:05:45.780
" Yeshua looked at me with those piercing eyes, smiled, and nodded in greeting.

00:05:45.780 --> 00:05:47.792
' Oh, that's beautiful.

00:05:47.792 --> 00:05:54.780
'I was allowed to see a glimpse of the aftermath of the Rapture here on Earth.

00:05:54.780 --> 00:06:00.435
I saw an unknown highway here in the United States.

00:06:19.960 --> 00:06:20.320
There were wrecked vehicles piled up everywhere, and some were on fire.

00:06:20.320 --> 00:06:41.600
I was given the understanding that the mass accidents were not so much because too many people had disappeared, but because a person in this car or that truck, even a public bus driver, had been taken, so it caused a chain reaction.

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:53.043
The strange thing revealed to me was that no one died; no one was allowed to die that day, as if placed as a testament to what had taken place.

00:06:53.043 --> 00:06:57.515
I then saw scientists and governments come together to try to explain the phenomenon.

00:07:00.805 --> 00:07:05.580
They came up with the conclusion that it was an alien invasion.

00:07:05.580 --> 00:07:16.373
Announcements were broadcast across television, cell phones, and the internet that we now knew the answer to the long-awaited question of whether or not we were alone.

00:07:16.373 --> 00:07:24.428
I was made aware that there was previously another type of plague/pandemic that had rolled out after COVID.

00:07:24.428 --> 00:07:25.800
' Pause.

00:07:45.459 --> 00:07:45.809
So, from what I'm understanding, this happens prior to the Rapture.

00:07:45.809 --> 00:07:50.959
There's another plague, and they are already planning all this.

00:07:50.959 --> 00:08:00.919
There's another pandemic, another thing I've warned you all is about to take place that the Lord keeps telling me about.

00:08:00.919 --> 00:08:05.206
They're already explaining away what's happening.

00:08:08.534 --> 00:08:11.010
I found that fascinating; it stood out to me.

00:08:11.010 --> 00:08:16.913
Go ahead, sorry to interrupt, I just have to interject sometimes.

00:08:16.913 --> 00:08:22.587
'They came up with the conclusion that this was an alien invasion.

00:08:22.587 --> 00:08:36.832
Announcements were broadcast across television, cell phones, and the internet that we now knew the answer to whether or not we were alone.

00:08:42.551 --> 00:08:48.959
I was made aware that there was previously another type of plague/pandemic that had rolled out after COVID.

00:08:54.880 --> 00:08:55.240
The pressure to get vaccinated and tracked had spread worldwide.

00:08:56.884 --> 00:09:05.326
The leaders used what had transpired as a bridge to introduce a new biometric system that would count and track the people.

00:09:05.326 --> 00:09:25.154
I heard leaders say that just as it was important during the pandemic that people worked together, it was even more so now, and that it was important to get the biometric ID so that they could keep track of everyone so that no one else could disappear.

00:09:25.154 --> 00:09:35.360
It became a worldwide mandate, and no citizen was allowed to function in society without it.

00:09:38.886 --> 00:09:42.080
In another scene, I was looking through a small window outside.

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:44.200
I saw complete chaos.

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:53.875
Everything was moving at rapid speed, as if someone had pressed the fast-forward button on a movie.

00:09:53.875 --> 00:09:59.408
I saw people in great distress: famine, disease, and much death.

00:09:59.408 --> 00:10:05.707
I saw meteor showers, fire falling upon the earth, massive earthquakes, and worldwide droughts.

00:10:05.707 --> 00:10:12.000
I saw military tanks and soldiers from many nations marching to war.

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:21.994
Finally, I saw the sky part and the Lord of Hosts with tens of thousands of His elite returning to Earth.

00:10:21.994 --> 00:10:37.258
I saw His foot touch down on the Mount of Olives, and as the ball of His foot touched the earth, a light blasted from Him and split the ground in two.

00:10:37.595 --> 00:10:38.946
The window then closed.

00:10:54.651 --> 00:10:54.994
The message that the Lord wants me to give to the church is that He is coming, and too many of us are still not ready.

00:10:54.994 --> 00:11:05.440
Many will be left behind simply because they did not search His word for the truth that He will call His bride from the earth.

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:12.615
There are too many who are distracted with recycled Earthbound prophecies from those who are seeking their kingdom in this life instead of the next.

00:11:12.615 --> 00:11:21.999
Too many are caught up in irrelevant things, debates, and arguments that they have deemed relevant yet do not bring in the harvest.

00:11:22.239 --> 00:11:29.640
The Lord said that the majority of those who are shouting "revival," their hearts are dark, and most don't even hear His voice.

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:43.827
The Lord said that a time of famine is upon the land—a famine for the word of the Lord.

00:11:43.827 --> 00:11:46.255
This is a season of quiet.

00:11:53.960 --> 00:12:01.337
The storm is already upon us, and warnings have already gone forth, so don't find yourself caught up in searching for the prophetic in people; what you will mostly find is that which is false.

00:12:01.337 --> 00:12:06.591
Seek Him, repent of the wickedness of your heart, and turn to Him, and He will set you free.

00:12:14.479 --> 00:12:14.719
The Lord said many are still battling with bitterness, unforgiveness, fear, perversion, and pride.

00:12:14.719 --> 00:12:18.310
Seek Him while you can still find Him, for the door is closing.

00:12:18.310 --> 00:12:23.026
As with all things, take this to prayer for confirmation.

00:12:23.026 --> 00:12:27.446
' That says it all.

00:12:27.446 --> 00:12:30.252
It's so exciting that Jesus is coming.

00:12:30.252 --> 00:12:41.326
Whenever she talked about the plague and how they usher in the biometric mark system to track everybody—they'll really introduce it when we are out of here.

00:12:41.326 --> 00:12:43.480
That's how they bring it on.

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:57.000
When I was trying to warn you about the Antichrist, and he stood at that table in Germany, in Berlin, and he was talking to all the world leaders—he's the one that came up with the plan.

00:13:04.275 --> 00:13:04.519
I know she talks about the scientists and people like that trying to explain it away, but he came on TV.

00:13:04.519 --> 00:13:07.559
Maybe we all see pieces.

00:13:10.013 --> 00:13:15.795
I don't see it all; I didn't see a lot of things about it, but she saw some things, and I see some things.

00:13:18.948 --> 00:13:25.100
I told you all about the other man that saw the angel coming, and that Mystery Babylon was New York City, and things were taking place with Mystery Babylon.

00:13:25.100 --> 00:13:30.388
That's what the Lord showed me, and she even talks about Mystery Babylon being New York.

00:13:30.388 --> 00:13:35.205
There's a lot of confirmation through God's people warning us of what's coming.

00:13:35.205 --> 00:13:39.084
All I know is I want to be out on the first load.

00:13:39.084 --> 00:13:40.169
Jesus is coming.

00:13:40.725 --> 00:13:47.880
I believe with all my heart we will have a Rapture of the church, a great harpazo, the catching away.

00:13:57.019 --> 00:13:57.199
I'm on that first load, and we will have the greatest feast of all time at the Marriage Supper of the Lamb.

00:13:57.199 --> 00:14:09.347
I've told you about it in videos below—the great feast that's about to take place, the lights, everything decorated so beautifully, the parade they're going to have for us, and the family members waiting for us to come home.

00:14:10.253 --> 00:14:13.759
I just want to encourage you all: it's not all doom and gloom.

00:14:13.759 --> 00:14:21.795
Yes, there are some bad days ahead, but as it's getting darker, the light's going to get brighter inside of us.

00:14:21.795 --> 00:14:25.759
Jesus lives on the inside of you and me.

00:14:26.079 --> 00:14:30.382
I want to encourage you today that Jesus is coming soon.

00:14:30.382 --> 00:14:39.320
I know there's a lot of people who say, 'Oh, roll up your rugs, it's not for a long time away,' but I'm telling you they're wrong.

00:14:41.195 --> 00:14:49.576
I believe with all my heart Jesus is coming sooner than people realize, and it's going to catch you off guard.

00:14:49.576 --> 00:14:52.320
It's going to shake everybody.

00:14:59.085 --> 00:14:59.510
I just wanted to come on here and encourage you, get you excited.

00:15:01.760 --> 00:15:02.810
I believe we will see this plague.

00:15:07.058 --> 00:15:07.329
I believe we will see a revival.

00:15:08.257 --> 00:15:14.600
I believe we will walk in those suits of white—that glory on us—and we will touch people and they will be healed by the power of God.

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:17.240
I'm always looking for Him to come quickly.

00:15:18.040 --> 00:15:24.620
We may have a couple years left, or five or six, but I'm telling you I have an urgency inside to be prepared.

00:15:24.620 --> 00:15:35.360
No man knows the day or the hour, but I'm telling you to be watching carefully and be looking for Him with your oil lamps full.

00:15:47.125 --> 00:15:47.434
That means being filled with the Spirit, seeking Him daily, not just one day a week on Sunday.

00:15:47.434 --> 00:15:48.360
Let's pray.

00:15:48.360 --> 00:15:51.790
Father, I thank You for every single person watching this video.

00:15:51.790 --> 00:15:56.120
